HOTA IND MFG CO said unconsolidated sales
in April rose 29.15% to NT$280,903,000 from NT$217,498,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            280,903          217,498    
YOY%              29.15%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,132,231         819,765    
YOY%              38.12% 
